                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>At his press conference of March 29, President Truman read a statement urging the
                    prompt passage by Congress of legislation to provide grain for India,
                    emphasizing the views expressed in his message of February 12. The text of the
                    President’s statement is printed in the Department of State <hi rend="italic"
                        >Bulletin</hi>, April 9, 1951, page 592.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
